::Killfest::

Killfest nods as he watches Scyther turn and walk from the room, the 
door closing behind him.

"I shall be there," he says to KitKat. The rest of his team exit his 
room, going back to theirs.



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, logomorph@h... wrote:
> ::KitKat::
> 
> She smiled and looked at Killfest. "Truely, you and your team are 
> amazing." She looked at the others and back to Killfest. "I have a 
> few other things to attend to. Please feel free to move about the 
> ship at your leasure. Tomorrow, we will hold council. I would be 
> honored if you attended." she said with a swet smile on her face.
